name: RFKTR's Black and White Manga
description:
Black and white manga TI.

If colors start to bleed in, just raise TI priority or add tags like 'greyscale', 'monochrome' and/or 'black and white' to your prompt.

If you like my work and want to support me, you can donate on Ko-fi, It will be greatly appreciated.

You should only give credit if you believe that my efforts warrant recognition.

Otherwise, just enjoy it.
